{"tid":568164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 日劇／甘草演員大杉漣突離世 】","createTime":"2018-02-21T13:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T22:48:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f9ac1192f081c5832d510caeaa5d927d17a0e2","tid":568164,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:58:01.000Z","msg":"日劇界資深演員大杉漣，因為急性心臟衰竭突然身亡，終年66歲。<br />\n<br />\n大杉漣原名大杉孝，1951年生於日本德島縣小松島市，1973年輟學投身演藝界。<br />\n<br />\n過去45年先後演山多套電影、劇集、舞台劇，包括多季《刑偵相棒》，飾演不同角色，第15季及第16季則飾演衣笠藤治一角。<br />\n<br />\n他亦與遠藤憲一、田口トモロヲ、寺島進、光石研、松重豊合演《Byplayers》，現時第二季仍在拍攝中，如今大杉漣突然離世，電視台表示第三集會如常播放，餘下兩集應該會改拍其他內容。<br />\n<br />\n（21022018）<br />\n<br />\n#yautaitung #游大東 #游大東影視筆記 #日劇 #大杉漣 OL干物女 紅眼 有台channel D 日藝評論節目 - J-House #刑偵相棒 #byplayers<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/215721_8afba7645cf31ef8191aea6ed1ff1b7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F215721_8afba7645cf31ef8191aea6ed1ff1b7b.png&h=81802f45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d85326c6e98be8a2586415835d93d6d3cc48003b","tid":568164,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢做開慈父角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5635f630285c2cd66478afbb91c5b424a9ee332","tid":568164,"uid":58374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"就係睇 byplayer 先記得佢個名<br />\n識咗佢一集就<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15313a29bd6c83458a1480629b84c6b4b93a052","tid":568164,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:12:33.000Z","msg":"咁就死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce638058efe1fa6bacd6b951b272102b4a3d8e3","tid":568164,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T20:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430ef3e236a1e021fc46854b22bd8ac327974273","tid":568164,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T22:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}